CSS Flexbox
Today's Focus: Flexbox Layout System
What I Learned:

display: flex and flex containers

justify-content, align-items, flex-direction

flex-wrap and gap property

Responsive navigation bar using flexbox

Practice Exercise: Responsive navbar and gallery

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: #2c3e50;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            color: white;
        }
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            list-style: none;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover {
            background: #34495e;
        }
        
        .gallery {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .gallery-item {
            width: 200px;
            height: 150px;
            background: #ecf0f1;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <h2>MyWebsite</h2>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Projects</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <div class="gallery">
        <div class="gallery-item">Project 1</div>
        <div class="gallery-item">Project 2</div>
        <div class="gallery-item">Project 3</div>
        <div class="gallery-item">Project 4</div>
        <div class="gallery-item">Project 5</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

Practice Question:
Create a pricing table with 3 columns using flexbox:

Each column should have equal width

Center content vertically and horizontally

Add a "Most Popular" badge on middle column

Make it responsive (stack vertically on mobile)

Use gap: 30px between columns


